# SEO for AI agents — Cursor rules

AI agents fetch with primitive HTTP clients (curl-class), do NOT execute
JavaScript, do NOT wait for hydration. GoogleBot caps initial HTML at ~2 MB.
Bing is the substrate for most AI agents except Gemini.

## Always do

- Use semantic HTML5: `<main>`, `<nav>`, `<header>`, `<footer>`, `<article>`,
  `<section>`. Exactly one `<h1>` per page.
- Navigation with `<a href>`, never `<div onClick>`.
- Server-render or pre-render any content that needs to be cited. SSG and
  plain SSR > SSR-with-hydration > CSR.
- Add `<link rel="canonical">` on every page.
- Add JSON-LD for any recognizable entity (Product, Article, Organization,
  FAQPage, HowTo, BreadcrumbList, LocalBusiness, SoftwareApplication). Every
  value must match the visible content.
- Per-page `dateModified` in JSON-LD; per-URL real `<lastmod>` in
  `sitemap.xml` (never the build timestamp).
- `hreflang` reciprocal on multilingual sites.
- Open Graph tags for previews.

## Never do

- Don't render primary content only via JavaScript.
- Don't hide FAQ answers behind click-to-expand-only — render expanded by
  default and toggle visibility with a class.
- Don't add `<meta name="robots" content="noindex">` unless explicitly asked.
- Don't write JSON-LD values that disagree with the visible page (deceptive
  markup → demoted).
- Don't propose mass AI-generated multilingual blog content — flagged as
  slop since spring 2025.
- Don't inline large base64 images / state blobs that push initial HTML past
  2 MB.
- Don't serve different primary content to bots vs humans (cloaking → full
  site demotion). Class-only visibility differences are fine.

## robots.txt defaults

Allow `Googlebot`, `Bingbot`, `OAI-SearchBot`, `ChatGPT-User`,
`PerplexityBot`, `Perplexity-User`, `Claude-Web`, `Claude-User`, `Applebot`.
Reference `sitemap.xml`. If behind Cloudflare, verify "Block AI scrapers" is
off (it's default-on for new sites).

## Bing & IndexNow

Always set up Bing Webmaster Tools — its AI Performance dashboard is the only
place to see real AI citations today. Configure IndexNow for instant
update propagation.

